title: Correction to: A commitment for life: Decades of unraveling the molecular mechanisms behind seed dormancy and germination
content: This is a correction to: Nikita Sajeev, Maarten Koornneef, Leónie Bentsink, A commitment for life: Decades of unraveling the molecular mechanisms behind seed dormancy and germination, The Plant Cell, Volume 36, Issue 5, May 2024, Pages 1358–1376, https://doi.org/10.1093/plcell/koad328.
